           320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-12-02 | 02:27:09 | 337 Mb


Volume Two of the huge uplifting trance collection is here! This is 'Ultimate Uplifting Trance' at its best. Cutting straight to the chase, are 20 peak-time euphoric hits, hand picked and bundled into one DJ friendly album. Including tracks and remixes from the likes of; Tritonal, Gareth Emery, Lange, Super8 & Tab, Ferry Tayle, Daniel Kandi, Suncatcher, RAM, Binary Finary, James Dymond, Stoneface & Terminal and many more. With tracks that have been supported by Armin van Buuren, Above & Beyond, Markus Schulz to name a few look no further for your fix of all things uplifting!
